			<item>
				<title>Watch the Knicks Parade Without NYC Traffic Chaos</title>
				<link>http://localhost:1313/blog/posts/how-to-watch-the-knicks-parade-on-nyc-traffic-surveillance-cameras/</link>
				<pubDate>Thu, 18 Jun 2026 13:29:44 +0000</pubDate>
				<guid>http://localhost:1313/blog/posts/how-to-watch-the-knicks-parade-on-nyc-traffic-surveillance-cameras/</guid>
				<description>&lt;h2 id=&#34;how-to-watch-the-knicks-parade-on-nyc-traffic-surveillance-cameras&#34; class=&#34;heading &#34;&gt;How to Watch the Knicks Parade on NYC Traffic Surveillance Cameras&lt;a href=&#34;#how-to-watch-the-knicks-parade-on-nyc-traffic-surveillance-cameras&#34; aria-labelledby=&#34;how-to-watch-the-knicks-parade-on-nyc-traffic-surveillance-cameras&#34;&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;!-- &lt;i class=&#34;fas fa-link anchor&#34;&gt;&lt;/i&gt; --&gt;&#xA;        &lt;svg class=&#34;svg-inline--fa fas fa-link anchor&#34; fill=&#34;currentColor&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34; role=&#34;img&#34; viewBox=&#34;0 0 576 512&#34;&gt;&lt;use href=&#34;#fas-link&#34;&gt;&lt;/use&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&amp;nbsp;&#xA;    &lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Are you a die-hard Knicks fan? Do you want to experience the excitement of the team&amp;rsquo;s ticker-tape parade without the crowds? We&amp;rsquo;ve got some great news for you - thanks to artist Morry Kolman, you can now watch the parade on NYC&amp;rsquo;s traffic surveillance cameras, and this time, the city&amp;rsquo;s Department of Transportation (DOT) isn&amp;rsquo;t demanding he stop. Here&amp;rsquo;s how you can catch the action.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
			</item>
			<item>
				<title>How to turn off AI in your Google Docs</title>
				<link>http://localhost:1313/blog/posts/how-to-turn-off-ai-in-your-google-docs/</link>
				<pubDate>Thu, 18 Jun 2026 13:26:34 +0000</pubDate>
				<guid>http://localhost:1313/blog/posts/how-to-turn-off-ai-in-your-google-docs/</guid>
				<description>&lt;p&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;img class=&#34;img-fluid &#34;&#xA;            src=&#34;http://localhost:1313/blog/blog/images/how-to-turn-off-ai-in-your-google-docs-2800x4197.png&#34;&#xA;             srcset=&#34;http://localhost:1313/blog/blog/images/how-to-turn-off-ai-in-your-google-docs-576x863.webp 576w, http://localhost:1313/blog/blog/images/how-to-turn-off-ai-in-your-google-docs-768x1151.webp 768w, http://localhost:1313/blog/blog/images/how-to-turn-off-ai-in-your-google-docs-992x1487.webp 992w, http://localhost:1313/blog/blog/images/how-to-turn-off-ai-in-your-google-docs-1200x1799.webp 1200w, http://localhost:1313/blog/blog/images/how-to-turn-off-ai-in-your-google-docs-1400x2099.webp 1400w, http://localhost:1313/blog/blog/images/how-to-turn-off-ai-in-your-google-docs-2800x4197.webp 2800w&#34; sizes=&#34;100vw&#34; height=&#34;4197&#34; width=&#34;2800&#34; alt=&#34;Featured Image&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;introduction-to-ai-in-google-docs&#34; class=&#34;heading &#34;&gt;Introduction to AI in Google Docs&lt;a href=&#34;#introduction-to-ai-in-google-docs&#34; aria-labelledby=&#34;introduction-to-ai-in-google-docs&#34;&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;!-- &lt;i class=&#34;fas fa-link anchor&#34;&gt;&lt;/i&gt; --&gt;&#xA;        &lt;svg class=&#34;svg-inline--fa fas fa-link anchor&#34; fill=&#34;currentColor&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34; role=&#34;img&#34; viewBox=&#34;0 0 576 512&#34;&gt;&lt;use href=&#34;#fas-link&#34;&gt;&lt;/use&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&amp;nbsp;&#xA;    &lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Google Docs has become an essential tool for individuals and businesses alike, providing a convenient and collaborative way to create and edit documents. Recently, Google introduced a new feature called &amp;ldquo;Gemini&amp;rdquo; which utilizes artificial intelligence (AI) to assist with writing tasks. While this feature can be helpful, some users may find the frequent &amp;ldquo;write with Gemini&amp;rdquo; pop-ups to be annoying and distracting. In this article, we will explore the reasons behind these pop-ups and provide a step-by-step guide on how to turn them off.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
			</item>
			<item>
				<title>Adobe Brings AI to Premiere</title>
				<link>http://localhost:1313/blog/posts/adobe-adds-its-ai-assistant-to-premiere-illustrator-and-indesign/</link>
				<pubDate>Thu, 18 Jun 2026 13:25:48 +0000</pubDate>
				<guid>http://localhost:1313/blog/posts/adobe-adds-its-ai-assistant-to-premiere-illustrator-and-indesign/</guid>
				<description>&lt;p&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;img class=&#34;img-fluid &#34;&#xA;            src=&#34;http://localhost:1313/blog/blog/images/adobe-adds-its-ai-assistant-to-premiere-illustrator-and-indesign-2800x1885.png&#34;&#xA;             srcset=&#34;http://localhost:1313/blog/blog/images/adobe-adds-its-ai-assistant-to-premiere-illustrator-and-indesign-576x388.webp 576w, http://localhost:1313/blog/blog/images/adobe-adds-its-ai-assistant-to-premiere-illustrator-and-indesign-768x517.webp 768w, http://localhost:1313/blog/blog/images/adobe-adds-its-ai-assistant-to-premiere-illustrator-and-indesign-992x668.webp 992w, http://localhost:1313/blog/blog/images/adobe-adds-its-ai-assistant-to-premiere-illustrator-and-indesign-1200x808.webp 1200w, http://localhost:1313/blog/blog/images/adobe-adds-its-ai-assistant-to-premiere-illustrator-and-indesign-1400x942.webp 1400w, http://localhost:1313/blog/blog/images/adobe-adds-its-ai-assistant-to-premiere-illustrator-and-indesign-2800x1885.webp 2800w&#34; sizes=&#34;100vw&#34; height=&#34;1885&#34; width=&#34;2800&#34; alt=&#34;Featured Image&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;introduction-to-adobes-firefly-ai-assistant&#34; class=&#34;heading &#34;&gt;Introduction to Adobe&amp;rsquo;s Firefly AI Assistant&lt;a href=&#34;#introduction-to-adobes-firefly-ai-assistant&#34; aria-labelledby=&#34;introduction-to-adobes-firefly-ai-assistant&#34;&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;!-- &lt;i class=&#34;fas fa-link anchor&#34;&gt;&lt;/i&gt; --&gt;&#xA;        &lt;svg class=&#34;svg-inline--fa fas fa-link anchor&#34; fill=&#34;currentColor&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34; role=&#34;img&#34; viewBox=&#34;0 0 576 512&#34;&gt;&lt;use href=&#34;#fas-link&#34;&gt;&lt;/use&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&amp;nbsp;&#xA;    &lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Adobe has announced a significant update to its Firefly AI assistant, which is designed to revolutionize the way creatives work with Adobe&amp;rsquo;s suite of applications. The updated Firefly AI assistant will be integrated into several key Adobe apps, including Premiere, Illustrator, InDesign, and Frame.io. This move is expected to enhance the overall user experience and streamline workflows for creatives.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
